name.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Address Autofill & Validator - Smart Form Filler

short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Easily autofill web forms with accurate address details using data from parsed text!

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Easily autofill web forms with accurate address details using data from parsed text! Our smart extension automatically fills in address fields Ideal for saving time on shipping forms.

Key features:

Autofill address forms with precision.
Supports various fields: address, contact details, and company info.
Works across multiple websites and languages.
Validates and corrects parsed data.
Boost your productivity and fill forms faster!
